Changes and updates to our privacy policy
This Privacy Policy may change from time to time and so you should revisit this page to keepinformed. When we materially change our Privacy Policy we will post the revised Privacy Policy on our Services and update the ‘last modified’ date at the bottom of this page. Your use of our Services following these changes means that you accept our revised Privacy Policy.
